etic-to-relativistic energy densities. The radio\nmodels also reveal a subtle effect whereby inverse Compton cooling leads to an\nincrease in emissivity as a result of the synchrotron characteristic frequency\nbeing significantly reduced. Finally, using the results of the radio analysis,\nwe estimate the surface magnetic field strengths to be $\\approx 0.3-52\\;$G.\n(Abridged)\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sun, 22 Jun 2014 09:48:11 GMT"}],"update_date":"2014-10-08"}
