ble tool that we used to i) avoid deadlock occurrences\non a dining philosophers benchmark, and ii) ensure the correct placement of\nrobots on a map.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sun, 22 Jun 2014 11:49:11 GMT"}],"update_date":"2014-06-24"}
